<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>

<body class="bg-dark text-light vh-100 d-flex align-items-center">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-5 col-lg-4">
                <div class="card bg-black border-info border-opacity-25 rounded-4 p-4 shadow-lg">
                    <div class="text-center mb-4">
                        <h1 class="h3 fw-bold text-info mb-2">관리자 로그인</h1>
                        <p class="text-secondary small">챌린지 관리를 위해 인증이 필요합니다.</p>
                    </div>

                    <form action="/admin/login" method="POST">
                        <div class="mb-4">
                            <label class="form-label text-secondary small">비밀번호</label>
                            <input type="password" name="password"
                                class="form-control bg-dark text-white border-secondary py-2" required autofocus>
                            <% if (error) { %>
                                <div class="text-danger small mt-2">
                                    <%= error %>
                                </div>
                                <% } %>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-info btn-lg w-100 text-white fw-bold py-2">로그인</button>
                    </form>

                    <div class="mt-4 text-center">
                        <a href="/" class="text-secondary small text-decoration-none">&larr; 메인으로 돌아가기</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>